{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "蒙面杀手在保定城外夜袭\"枪剑无敌\"裴氏双杰，以融合少林、武当、峨嵋多派武功的高超身手将二人击毙，夺走异宝碧玉蟾蜍。此后数月，蒙面人连杀两河十六家镖局中十三位总镖头，武林为之震恐。雄风镖局总镖头中州一剑欧阳平之赶到北京，与飞龙镖局总镖头龙形八掌檀明商议对策。当夜蒙面人潜入飞龙镖局，欧阳平之追出迎敌，最终与蒙面人同归于尽。檀明为欧阳平之披麻戴孝，收养十三位镖头遗孤，声望更隆。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_xiao_jing_han_de_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "短小精悍的汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好冷！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_xiao_jing_han_de_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "短小精悍的汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，他怎地会在这里？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shou_men_zu_zi",
      "speaker_name": "守门卒子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子可真棒！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面骑士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎地还不来？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yang",
      "speaker_name": "裴扬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前面的像就是那话儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们将马放慢一些吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yang",
      "speaker_name": "裴扬",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "老哥借光，让个道给我们走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面骑士",
      "listener": "char_pei_yang",
      "text": "两位敢情就是两河闻名的'枪剑无敌'裴氏双杰吧？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "朋友好厉害的眼光，不错，在下就是弧形剑裴元，这就是家兄钩镰枪裴扬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "朋友深夜在此相候，莫非对我兄弟有什么指教吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面骑士",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "我听说裴二侠性情豪爽，如今一见，果然是快人快语。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面骑士",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "既然如此，我在明人面前，也不必说暗话，今日来此，我也没有什么别的用意，只不过是想向两位讨一样东西罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "要向我兄弟要东西，还不简单得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "只是朋友也该亮个万儿，要知道，我兄弟的东西，却不是随便要得的呢。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面骑士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要的不是别的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面骑士",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "就是贵兄弟头上的脑袋，和两位怀中的玩意。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "裴二侠为着什么事这么好笑？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "我裴家兄弟出来闯荡江湖十余年，还没有人敢在我哥儿俩面前说过难听的话，朋友，你凭着些什么，就敢在我哥儿俩面前这样卖狂，你敢情也是活得不大耐烦了吧？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yang",
      "speaker_name": "裴扬",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "朋友！咱们废话少说，还是手底下见个真章吧。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_pei_yang",
      "text": "好，好，裴氏双杰果然都是好汉，兄弟今天若不成全你们，从此武林中就没有兄弟这号人物。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "就像阁下这号藏头露尾的鼠辈也能称上是'人物'的话，那武林中的人物，也未免太多了些吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "两位请过来吧，这里清清静静，用来做两位的葬身之地，那是再好也没有了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yang",
      "speaker_name": "裴扬",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "朋友端的好身手，我姓裴的走遍大江南北，可是像朋友这样的身手，我姓裴的倒真还少见，想必朋友也是武林中成名立万的好汉，我姓裴的这次保的镖，朋友既然知道了，也该知道来路，我姓裴的万万担不起这个责任，朋友若看得起我姓裴的，亮个万儿，高高手，青山不改，绿水长流，日后我姓裴的总有报答朋友之处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_pei_yang",
      "text": "大哥，和这种鼠辈废话于什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "贵兄弟还是一齐上吧，省得我一个个地动手费事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "当然，我兄弟和鼠辈动手，从来不讲武林规矩，因为你不配。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_pei_yuan",
      "text": "好，好，我不配！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "裴氏双杰",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "裴元",
      "listener": "char_meng_mian_qi_shi",
      "text": "我兄弟和你有什么仇怨？你竟下得了如此辣手！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ping_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳平之",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "北京城里果然是人杰地灵，今天我老头子总算开了眼啦。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ping_zhi",
      "text": "欧阳老前辈稍为歇息一下，等会儿晚辈再陪您到别处逛逛。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ping_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳平之",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀老弟快别这样称呼，可把我老头折煞了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ping_zhi",
      "text": "老前辈远道而来，晚辈真惭愧得很，本来晚辈早该去拜访您的——",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ping_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳平之",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "这有啥子关系，我也是顺便到北京城来耍子的，那小子这几个月虽然搞得天翻地覆，可也还不值得我老头子巴巴地从河南跑来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    }
  ],
